WEBVTT

20:55.130 --> 20:57.740 line:80%
Your Majesty, I have a proposal.

20:58.280 --> 20:59.910 line:80%
Grand Tutor, please go ahead.

20:59.910 --> 21:00.720 line:80%
Your Majesty,

21:01.070 --> 21:03.150 line:80%
the weather has been erratic this year.

21:03.150 --> 21:05.680 line:80%
The land is barren,
and the crops have failed.
